ingress.answerMinQuestions: If you want to find the {candidatePlural} and {partyPlural} that agree with you the most, {questionsLink} first.
ingress.questionsLinkText: answer at least {numQuestions, plural, =1 {one question} other {# questions}}

noNominations.title: There are no candidates or parties in your constituency who have responded to the Election Compass
noNominations.content: You can review the questions if you wish, but results cannot be displayed.

someNominations.title: The number of candidates who have completed the election test in this municipality is five or fewer.
someNominations.content: The results should therefore be interpreted with caution, as they may not provide a complete picture of the full field of candidates. Take the test anyway to see how much you agree with the young candidates in your municipality.

fewCandidatesWarning: Note: The number of candidates who have completed the election compass in this municipality or region is limited. The results should therefore be interpreted with caution, as they do not necessarily provide a comprehensive picture of the entire field of candidates.
